Students actively engage with exhibitors, holding resumes in branded folders while comparing promotional items like tote bags filled with notebooks, pens, water bottles, and phone chargers distributed by recruiters. Event staff scan registrations and log attendance metrics, while career counselors assist students in identifying applicable industries and emphasize maintaining eye contact during interactions, especially for international students seeking visa sponsorship advice. Concurrently, workshops on networking etiquette and an alumni panel discussing technical interview strategies occur in adjacent classrooms. As the event progresses, students line up for registration, sign-up sheets fill quickly, and post-event survey links are displayed near the exit.
